<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٨ - وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ <span style="color:#950000">" اتَّقُوا الْيَهُودَ وَالْهُنُودَ وَلَوْ بِسَبْعِينَ بَطْنًا "</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٦٩ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" إِنَّ فِي بِلادٍ أَوْرَاقًا مِثْلَ آذَانِ الْخَيْلِ فَكُلُوا مِنْهَا فَإِنَّ فِيهَا مَنْفَعَةً "</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٧٠ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" قَلْبُ الْمُؤْمِنِ عَرْشُ اللَّهِ "</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٧١ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" الْجُمُعَةُ حَجُّ الْمَسَاكِينِ "</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>